law_name: THE SUPREME COURT (NUMBER OF JUDGES) ACT

sections.body: (1) This Act may be called the Supreme Court (Number of Judges) Act, 1997. (2) It shall come into force at once.

sections.section_title: Maximum number of Supreme Court Judges other than Chief Justice
sections.body: The maximum number of Judges of the Supreme Court of Pakistan other than the Chief Justice shall be up to thirty-three.
